    "body": "After talking with @chadyj and @annadanchenko, to keep it simple we can use the following two reference devices:\r\n\r\n- iOS: iPhone 6s\r\n- Android: Samsung Galaxy S6\r\n\r\nThis doesn't mean \"if it works on these everything is fine perf wise\", it means \"if it doesn't work on these we have a big problem\" (and same goes for S6+/6s+ of course).\r\n\r\nMarking this issue as done for now as getting more high-granular view isn't necessary from 55/Fast Status POV AFAIK. QA already have their own process for doing these checks which involve real user data and a multitude of devices.",
